            </p>
            <button 
              onClick={() => {
                setSubmitted(false);
                setFormData({ name: '', phone: '', category: '선택해 주세요', content: '', privacy: false });
              }}
              className="px-10 py-4 bg-blue-900 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-blue-800 transition-all shadow-lg"
            >
              확인
